<section>
  <h2>Rush</h2>
  <p><strong>Week One: </strong>Sigma Phi Delta brothers will be boothing at WOW Showcase as well as in the UU Plaza. Feel free to drop by and meet some of us and pick up a flyer of events. We will be recruiting for our fraternity's rush that starts the following week.</p>
  <p><strong>Week Two: </strong>Rush week begins and ends. Each day there will be a different event set up for Cal Poly students to come and get to know the brothers. This week is also our chance to meet people who we will potentially invite to join Sigma Phi Delta. The details of these events are listed below:</p>
  <h2>Pre Rush Week Events</h2>
  <p><strong>Meet and Greet &dash; Santa Lucia</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Time: 6pm on Thursday, Sept. 29th</li>
    <li>Location: Santa Lucia Commons</li>
    <li>Hear a brief presentation about our organization and meet active brothers. Free pizza!</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Walk to SloDoCo</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Time: 4pm on Friday, Sept. 30th</li>
    <li>Location: Dexter Lawn</li>
    <li>Who doesn't love donuts? Come join us in a walk from Cal Poly campus to SloDoCo and back. This is a good opportunity to get to know the brothers and other friends to the organization.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>Rush Week Events</h2>
  <p><strong>Day One: Kickoff Barbecue</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Time: 6pm on Monday, Oct. 3rd</li>
    <li>Location: Diablo Lawn, North Mountain</li>
    <li>Help us kick off our recruitment week by enjoying some grilled dogs and interacting with brothers in sports and conversation.</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Day Two: A Night at the Castle</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Time: 6pm on Tuesday, Oct. 4th</li>
    <li>Location: Engineering IV Lawn (rides provided)</li>
    <li>This is our first ever event at our main house off campus. There will be games and sports, as well as a mini project expo and other items specifically hightlighting the work members have put into our organization.</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Day Three: Internship Panel</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Time: 6pm on Wednesday, Oct. 5th</li>
    <li>Location: Building 33 Room 286</li>
    <li>Learn what it is like to work in industry. A number of our brothers will be discussing different projects and challenges they have faced in recent summers and jobs.</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Day Four: Burgers and Bros</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Time: 6pm on Thursday, Oct. 6th</li>
    <li>Location: PAC Circle (rides provided)</li>
    <li>Sylvester's is a restaurant in Los Osos popular for its delicious, greasy burgers. We will be transporting actives and rushees to the location to enjoy a half-price meal as the final day of open recruitment.</li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>The Weekend: </strong>Be sure to keep Friday night, all day Saturday and all day Sunday open for fraternity purposes. If you are selected to join, these will be important days.</p>
  <p><strong>Please direct any questions to Recruitment Chairman Brandon Kelley: recruitment.spd.calpoly@gmail.com</strong></p>
